added.title: Real Art
added.description: After Starfire buys an ugly painting, the Titans take her to the museum so she can experience real art.

added.title: Just a Little Patience…Yeah…Yeah
added.description: Robin tries to teach the other Titans to have patience.

added.title: Encore'tney
added.description: When Courtney turns to a magical datebook to help her achieve perfection, she's trapped in a never ending loop until a friend teaches her a valuable lesson.

added.title: Life of Pie
added.description: When Izzy, Jude and Owen accidentally bring a pizza to life they do everything they can to help him find a new purpose in life other than being eaten.

added.title: Stay Goth, Poodle Girl, Stay Goth
added.description: Gwen accidentally brings a pink stuffed pony she loves to daycare and spends the day denying it's hers.

added.title: Gum and Gummer
added.description: Beth gets her gum stuck in Leshawna's hair and has to get it out - without Leshawna finding out it's there.

added.title: Invasion of the Booger Snatchers
added.description: Harold believes that the picture day photographer is somehow turning the kids into well behaved zombies.

added.title: Vengeance Is Mine!
added.description: Aspheera arrives at the Monastery of Spinjitzu and confronts Wu, forcing one of the ninja to make a heroic sacrifice.

added.title: A Cold Goodbye
added.description: Having learned Zane is not dead, Master Wu prepares to go after him, but Lloyd and the other ninja take matters into their own hands and defy their Master.

added.title: The Never-Realm
added.description: The ninja arrive in the Never-Realm where they quickly find themselves overwhelmed. Luckily, they are taken in by a tribe of Ice Fishers who tell them Zane has been imprisoned by the evil Ice Emperor.

added.title: Fire Maker
added.description: The Ice Emperor learns of the ninja's arrival and sends his Blizzard Samurai warriors to destroy them and the villagers who sheltered them.

added.title: An Unlikely Ally
added.description: Lloyd runs afoul of the Ice Emperor's Blizzard Samurai but is rescued by a strange wolf with whom an unlikely friendship develops.

added.title: #DCSuperHeroBoys Part 1
added.description: What begins as a simple vandalism investigation becomes an all-out turf war when the team encounters a powerful trio of Kryptonians bent on world domination, and, perhaps even worse, a rival team of SUPER HERO BOYS!

added.title: #DCSuperHeroBoys Part 2
added.description: What begins as a simple vandalism investigation becomes an all-out turf war when the team encounters a powerful trio of Kryptonians bent on world domination, and, perhaps even worse, a rival team of SUPER HERO BOYS!

added.title: #GothamCon
added.description: A fun day for Barbara Gordon and her bestie Harleen Quinzel (at Gotham City's annual geekfest, the Annual Convention of Gotham City Enthusiats!) is turned on its head when, out of nowhere, the villainous Harley Quinn shows up to wreak havoc! Lucky for everyone, Batgirl just happens to be in the area...

added.title: #Frenemies Part 1
added.description: Batgirl's worlds collide when her best friend from Gotham City moves to Metropolis. Meanwhile, Catwoman is making some new friends of her own.

added.title: #Frenemies Part 2
added.description: Batgirl's worlds collide when her best friend from Gotham City moves to Metropolis. Meanwhile, Catwoman is making some new friends of her own.

added.title: Schnorp
added.description: The Thunderkittens plug a new video game cartridge into Snarf only to learn that it didn't load a game, it loaded a whole new personality into their pal! Meet Schnorp, a kind Swedish man who loves the beauty of nature and collecting berries! Schnorp is loads of fun, but we're gonna want Snarf back, right?

added.title: Berb-cules
added.description: The ThunderCats finally sit the Berbils down and tell them they really shouldn't be building things for the Mutants anymore, it's time for the Berbils to stand up for themselves. The Berbils take this advice way too far and build a giant, building-sized, Berbil named Berbcules. Berb-cules takes back everything the Berbils ever built for the Mutants and everything they ever built for the ThunderCats! Now Panthro has to figure out a way to a defeat the most powerful invention the best little builders have ever built!

added.title: Pumm-Ra
added.description: Mumm-Ra plans to disguise himself as a Thunderian and infiltrate Cats' Lair, but the Ancient Spirits of Evil are mad at him and won't give him any magic today. No matter, Mumm-Ra knows what a ThunderCat looks like so he slaps on some awful, unconvincing, cat make up and heads to Cats' Lair to introduce himself!

added.title: King of the Machines
added.description: Panthro gets insecure when he finds out Barbastella has a history of dating royalty, so he tries to impress her by becoming "King of the Machines" and giving all the appliances in the Cats' Lair artificial intelligence.

added.title: Sword Heist
added.description: When a local sword shop sells an ultra powerful sword to Ratar-O, Lion-O decides he has to steal it before Ratar-O can come pick it up. Unfortunately Lion-O is completely against stealing, but luckily he knows someone who loves to steal, Lion-S!

added.title: Eclipsorr
added.description: Third Earth's sun is being blocked out by the Eclipsor Corporation, an amoral company that wants to sell its energy for a profit. The ThunderCats can't do anything about it because they don't have a spaceship, yet!

added.title: Thirst for Power
added.description: Axel and his toys deploy the Joyride in a "ship" to "ship" battle against Dr. Nautilus, who has punctured a water main to flood the sewers and established himself as "Admiral Nautilus."

added.title: Party On
added.description: As Zoe preps Cleo LeBall's birthday party, Axel and the team run damage control against a jealous crasher - Princess SugarSalt, who has turned the decorations and gifts into instruments of chaos!

added.title: Bringing Up Baby
added.description: Zoe leaves Axel in charge of the school project - watching over an infant simulator doll - but when MadCap brings the doll to life, Axel and the team must stop the baby without damaging it or risk getting a failing grade!

added.title: Stretched Too Thin
added.description: After a new combo-move leaves Masko permanently limp, Axel and the team must help the fallen luchador get his stretch back.

added.title: From Below
added.description: Axel juggles looking after Luka and defending the house from Dr. Nautilus's latest abomination, a tentacle monster that attacks from every drain, pipe, and faucet in the building!

added.title: All Jungled Up/Outer Demons
added.description: All Jungled Up: Still lost in Vestroia the AO experience mind altering effects of the nearby Core Cell and come face to face with the Bakuzon monster Tiko./Outer Demons: The AO find the doorway out of Vestroia only to learn they have entered a mirror world of their own imagining created by the Core Cell.

added.title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
added.description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

added.title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
added.description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

added.title: It's Chemistry, Man
added.description: Chemistry Man lays siege to Silicon Central when he discovers that his replacement, Miss CHO, has been presented with a teaching award.

added.title: Flower Power
added.description: Mega Man must battle Wood Man for the fate of the Corpse Flower, a rare and noxious bloom that's stinking up all of Silicon City.

added.title: Enemy of My Enemy
added.description: When a grudge match between Fire Man and Namagem threatens to level Silicon City, Mega Man must intervene and ultimately choose a side to prevent collateral damage.

added.title: Old School
added.description: Mega Man must stop Chaotique from making Silicon Central disappear, as in literally erasing the school at a subatomic level, while learning life lessons from a rambling old-bot named Hal.

added.title: This Is Not a Drill
added.description: Mega Man and Dr. Light must set aside a father-son disagreement to stop Drill Man from taking revenge on his own overbearing father.

added.title: Raritos de Pascua
added.description: Llegó la Pascua y el Hada de los Dientes intenta apoderarse de la festividad.

added.title: La Venganza es Mia
added.description: Aspheera llega al Monasterio de Spinjitzu y se enfrenta a Wu, obligando a uno de los ninjas a hacer un sacrificio heroico.

added.title: Una Fria Despedida
added.description: Habiendo aprendido que Zane no está muerto, el Maestro Wu se prepara para ir tras él, pero Lloyd y el otro ninja toman el asunto en sus propias manos y desafían a su Maestro.

added.title: El Reino del Jamas
added.description: Los ninja llegan al Never-Realm donde rápidamente se sienten abrumados. Afortunadamente, son recibidos por una tribu de pescadores de hielo que les dicen que Zane ha sido encarcelado por el malvado Emperador de hielo.

added.title: #SuperHeroBoys Parte 1
added.description: Lo que comienza como una simple investigación por vandalismo, se transforma en una lucha territorial cuando las chicas encuentran un poderoso trío de kryptonianos decididos a dominar el mundo, y lo que es peor... iun grupo de Super Hero Boys!
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #SuperHeroBoys Parte 2
added.description: Lo que comienza como una simple investigación por vandalismo, se transforma en una lucha territorial cuando las chicas encuentran un poderoso trío de kryptonianos decididos a dominar el mundo, y lo que es peor... iun grupo de Super Hero Boys!
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #LaConvencionDeGotham
added.description: Un divertido día para Barbara Gordon y su mejor amiga Harley Quinzel en la Convención Anual de Gotham City, es puesto cabeza abajo cuando, de la nada, ila malvada Harley Quinn aparece para sembrar el caos! Por suerte para todos, Batgirl se encuentra casualmente en el área...
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Princesa gotica
added.description: Gwen lleva por accidente un pony de peluche rosado que le encanta a la guardería, y pasa todo el día negando que es suyo.

added.title: Atrapados en la Jungla
added.description: Aún perdidos en Vestroia, Los Fantásticos experimentan los efectos de la Célula Núcleo que altera sus cuerpos, y se encuentran cara a cara con el monstruo Bakugan, Tiko.

added.title: Goma pegajosa
added.description: A Beth se le atasca la goma de mascar en el cabello de Leshawna y tiene que sacarla- sin que Leshawna descubra que está ahí.

added.title: Demonios Internos
added.description: Los Fantásticos encuentran la forma de salir de Vestroia, pero descubren que en realidad están en un mundo paralelo.

added.title: Una Extrana Conexion
added.description: Drago lidera a los Bakugan contra la amenaza de Tiko, para proteger una poderosa fuente de energía.

added.title: Invasion de los mocos ladrones
added.description: Harold cree que el fotógrafo del día de la foto oficial está convirtiendo a los niños en zombies que se portan bien.

added.title: La Celula Nucleo
added.description: Los Fantásticos defienden la Célula Núcleo de un ataque de Tiko, y en el último intento de Dan por salvarla, él y Drago logran liberar un nuevo poder.

added.title: Hogar, Dulce Hogar
added.description: Los Fantásticos vuelven a casa y se dan cuenta de que el tiempo no ha pasado. Pronto descubren que su conocimiento acerca de las batallas ha aumentado de forma exponencial.

added.title: Un Golpe de Ternura
added.description: Después de derrotar a Strata, Los Fantásticos se dan cuenta de que no volvieron solos, sino con un Bakugan parecido a un panda que les dará muchos problemas.

added.title: Desde las Profundidades
added.description: iAxel hace malabares cuidando a Luka y defendiendo la casa de la última abominación del Dr. Nautilus, un monstruo tentáculo que ataca desde cada drenaje, tubería y grifo del edificio!

added.title: El Hacedor de Fuego
added.description: El Emperador de Hielo se entera de la llegada de los ninjas y envía a sus guerreros Samurais Blizzard a destruirlos, y a todos los aldeanos que los albergaron.

added.title: Estirado Demasiado Delgado
added.description: Después de que un nuevo movimiento combinado deja a Masko permanentemente flácido, Axel y el equipo deben ayudar al luchador caído a recuperarse.

added.title: #AmiEnemigas - Segunda Parte
added.description: Los mundos de Batgirl colisionan cuando su mejor amiga de Gotham City se muda a Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Catwoman también hace nuevos amigos...
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #AmiEnemigas - Primera Parte
added.description: Los mundos de Batgirl colisionan cuando su mejor amiga de Gotham City se muda a Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Catwoman también hace nuevos amigos…
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Un Aliado Peculiar
added.description: Lloyd se enfrenta a los Samurais Blizzard del Emperador de Hielo, pero es rescatado por un lobo extraño con quien desarrolla una amistad peculiar.

added.title: Criando Bebe
added.description: Zoe deja a Axel a cargo del proyecto escolar, vigilando una muñeca simulador de bebés, pero cuando MadCap da vida a la muñeca, iAxel y el equipo deben detener al bebé sin dañarlo o correr el riesgo de obtener una calificación reprobatoria!

added.title: Que Comience la Fiesta
added.description: Mientras Zoe prepara la fiesta de cumpleaños de Cleo LeBall, Axel y el equipo controlan los daños contra una estrelladora celosa: ila princesa SugarSalt, que ha convertido las decoraciones y los regalos en instrumentos de caos!

added.title: Sed de Poder
added.description: Axel y sus juguetes despliegan el Joyride en una batalla de "barco" a "barco" contra el Dr. Nautilus, quien ha perforado una tubería de agua para inundar las alcantarillas y se ha establecido como "Almirante Nautilus".
